Stock management software

The idea is to work in a program about stock. (It is specially designed for companies like SACDE)
Features list:
todo -products (Add, lookup, Edit, Remove) With description box
todo -receipts(Add, lookup, Remove)
todo -receipt consists of: number, date, item(s) & quantity, worker, sector
todo -receipts edits stocks numbers
todo -suppliers(Add, lookup, Edit, Remove)
todo -suppliers consists of Name, Address, email, phone, description
todo -Workers(Add, lookup, Edit, Remove)
todo -workers consists of Name, ID, his/her superior
todo -tables of items loan, workers with items,
todo -Table of suppliers, and data of contact
todo -a module to print receipts in PDF files, for lending
todo -a Visual application



